6.6.3 Price forecasting
Power price forecasting (spot electricity markets) shall be provided to enable Market
Operation wing to make efficient procurement decisions. RTM/DAM, Congestion-ATC NEWR-SR, S1-S2S3, Within SR, etc. shall be the factors affecting Price forecast.
The following factors, which are critical inthe forecast of the price pattern, shall
113
